@node Registration

Registation

Limit:

The only shareware limitation is that only 20 hosts can be stored.
On registered version the limit in variable.

How to register:

Send me a mail with translations,bugreports of new ideas for
Hostjunkey. Or send me letter via post with some money to my address
and you e-mail in the letter. I don`t think that many people
send me money, but it`s not so important for me. Normaly I
would release it as freeware, but i wanna some response for
my work to continue HostJunkey. And i think it`s not too much
to write a little mail for this useful tool. Also it`s easier
to send a mail than crack HostJunkey or leech a released keyfile...
if its really happen. :)

